        "TileImage": "$($repository 79359280-26f8-4dc3-8dc5-f3ff918fbeaa).Image",
        "Description": "Frank Schmidt was an avid collector of monarchs among other things. Of course, his novelties resulted in a resident of Whittleton Creek to do him in, clipping his wings before he was going to blossom and move elsewhere and open his own museum.\r\rResidents are getting shifty, and want to explore Schmidt&apos;s death further.\r\rOf course, this is just like picking wings off a butterfly.",
